# Rapid MVP Creator Platform - Implementation Plan

## Architecture Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["Next.js App Router"]
        Auth["Auth Pages"]
        FanDash["Fan Dashboard"]
        CreatorDash["Creator Dashboard"]
        Store["Redemption Store"]
        Feed["Content Feed"]
    end
    
    subgraph Backend["API Routes"]
        AuthAPI["Auth API"]
        WalletAPI["Wallet API"]
        ContentAPI["Content API"]
        StripeAPI["Stripe Webhook"]
        GamificationAPI["Gamification Engine"]
        RedemptionAPI["Redemption API"]
    end
    
    subgraph Supabase["Supabase"]
        PG["PostgreSQL"]
        SupaAuth["Auth"]
        RLS["Row Level Security"]
    end
    
    subgraph External["External Services"]
        Stripe["Stripe Checkout"]
    end
    
    Frontend --> Backend
    Backend --> Supabase
    StripeAPI --> Stripe
```

## Database Schema

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `profiles` | User profile with role (fan/creator) |
| `wallets` | Token and points balances |
| `token_packages` | Predefined Stripe purchase packages |
| `token_transactions` | Token purchase/spend history |
| `point_transactions` | Points earn/spend history |
| `posts` | Creator content (public/gated) |
| `post_unlocks` | Fan-post unlock records |
| `post_likes` | Likes on posts |
| `post_comments` | Comments on posts |
| `redemption_items` | Creator store items |
| `redemption_orders` | Fan redemption orders |
| `daily_rewards` | Track daily login rewards |

