## Implementation Phases

### Phase 1: Project Setup & Auth
- [x] Initialize Next.js with Tailwind
- [ ] Configure Supabase client
- [ ] Auth pages (login, register)
- [ ] Role-based middleware
- [ ] Protected routes

### Phase 2: Database & Wallet
- [ ] Create SQL schema
- [ ] Wallet display components
- [ ] Transaction history

### Phase 3: Stripe Integration
- [ ] Token packages
- [ ] Checkout session API
- [ ] Webhook handler

### Phase 4: Content System
- [ ] Post creation (creator)
- [ ] Content feed (fan)
- [ ] Token-gated unlocking
- [ ] Likes & comments

### Phase 5: Gamification
- [ ] Points engine
- [ ] Daily login rewards
- [ ] Action-based points
- [ ] Rate limiting

### Phase 6: Redemption Store
- [ ] Item creation (creator)
- [ ] Store browsing (fan)
- [ ] Point redemption

### Phase 7: Dashboards & Polish
- [ ] Fan dashboard
- [ ] Creator dashboard
- [ ] Analytics
- [ ] Leaderboard

## Security Checklist
- [ ] All balance updates in database transactions
- [ ] Stripe webhook signature verification
- [ ] RLS policies on all tables
- [ ] Rate limiting on gamification APIs
- [ ] Server-side validation for all operations
- [ ] No frontend trust for balance updates
